data.description: Imagine having your coffee every morning on this new Trex Deck with stunning views of Beautiful Deschutes River. Heat pump with AC, new in 2021. New bathroom w/ Heated tile floor, walk in tile shower. All appliances stay, including newer stackable washer/dryer and New Fridge 2023. Hardwood flooring, skylights, in almost every room. Two very large bedrooms, in main house with lots of closet space. Roof 2017.  Addl Finished 1bd 600 sq ft with slider, heated building w/new high end flooring great for a ADU, that was the plan before Sellers had to move, easy to add a bathroom,3bd septic. In addition, 24x8 insulated storage sheds, 20x12 wood shop, and a nice metal carport 22x24. Deck is wired for hot tub 220V w/a view! Get Equity NOW, NEW PRICE!
